{
  "id": "adv_event_2510_01_01",
  "title": "生徒会長、\n鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――今から数か月前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.1666666071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、聞いて！\nうち、生徒会長になります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.0666666071,
      "endTime": 7.5480950396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7333333691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待って！？　突然そんなこと言われても\nすぐに応援は出来ないわ。アイドル活動もあるのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333333691,
      "endTime": 16.0457826335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.2310209632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "それは分かってる。でも、学生として「今」しか\n出来ひんこともあるやん。それが生徒会長やと思うねん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2310209632,
      "endTime": 24.9364403128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきHRで「生徒会長さんの転校が急に決まったから\n生徒会長選挙を来月頭にやる」って聞いてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1310212175,
      "endTime": 34.1060318987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.2976871212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、それは私も聞いたわ\n確か今の会長は進学コースの三年生だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2976871212,
      "endTime": 42.008593912900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.1938322425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、うちら芸能コースやし学年もちゃうけど\n廊下ですれ違ったら挨拶してくれて、ええ人やった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1938322425,
      "endTime": 51.373378407900006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5604989092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "この間の全校集会でもどんな思いで活動してるか\n話しとったやろ？　それを聞いてうち、心が震えてん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5604989092,
      "endTime": 61.105782036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.2938328107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、うちが生徒会長さんの意志を継いで\nこの学校をより良くしていきたい……そう思うんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2938322425,
      "endTime": 69.6714966178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.8604989092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "優……分かったわ。それなら私も全力で優が生徒会長に\nなれるようにサポートするわ。一緒に頑張りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8604989092,
      "endTime": 79.3005669633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生徒会選挙当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3524725278,
      "endTime": 81.41913868590001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 81.5191386859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "生徒みんなに、漫画みたいな、輝く青春を送ってほしい\n無駄じゃない、通って良かったって思える場所にしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3858047843,
      "endTime": 93.0656685233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そのために、うちが生徒会長になったら\n誰でも、なんでも話を聞かせてほしいと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.252471451,
      "endTime": 101.0146482507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolgymstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolgymstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2524709423
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "友達にはちょっと話しにくいとか、相談しにくいとか\n誰に話していいか分からん時、うちに話してほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2524709423,
      "endTime": 110.7324712475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "あなたの学校生活の主人公は、あなたなんです\nあなたが輝くためのお手伝いをさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.919137609,
      "endTime": 118.90421861419999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8191407204,
      "endTime": 120.8524771054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 120.8858104388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "見て見て、瑠依ちゃん！\nうち生徒会長っぽくなってきたと思わん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7524755199,
      "endTime": 126.9550834377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 123.6191391945
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 127.1524755199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ふざけてる暇はないわよ。ほら、この書類の山を見て\n生徒達からの相談事がこんなに沢山溜まっているのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1524755199,
      "endTime": 136.0024757105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 136.1877140402
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "優が生徒会長に就任してからまだ一か月も経ってない\nというのに……私も手伝うから一つずつ解決しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1877140402,
      "endTime": 145.71998142,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12217.502717299993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 145.9052197496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "いつもおおきにな。えーっと、部の立ち上げ申請が\nぎょうさんきとる……顧問の先生を探さなあかんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9052197496,
      "endTime": 156.4024310152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 156.6052197496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "前にも似たような問題があったわね。その時にまとめた\n現状手の空いている先生のリストがあったはずよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6052197496,
      "endTime": 164.7789837877,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12992.332708899994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 164.9642221172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "それ使って先生に声掛けて回れば解決しそうやね\nこっちは学食にハーフサイズの追加を希望、か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.9642221172,
      "endTime": 176.53143307759998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 176.7308887839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、学食の改善はある程度出来たんやけど\nハーフサイズの要望は未だにぎょうさんきとるなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.7308887839,
      "endTime": 185.4142248512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 185.5975585024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "これだけ生徒達から声が上がるのなら追加で交渉する\n価値はありそうね……校長先生に相談してみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.5975585024,
      "endTime": 193.8799860995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_studentcouncilroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "seitokai",
      "startTime": 194.065224429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
